article.headline: Utah Valley St. 77, Sacramento St. 52
article.story: OREM, Utah -- Holton Hunsaker scored 23 points and Isiah Williams added 19 as Utah Valley beat Sacramento State 77-52 on Saturday night. Justin Baker added 11 points and Jordan Swarbrick 10 for the Wolverines (4-3). Walter Jackson had 13 points for the Hornets (2-5). Utah Valley never trailed and pounced early, building a 22-8 lead after 7 1/2 minutes. The Wolverines' smallest lead after that was six points.
